N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4122.23 - Daily double terms

State Regulations

In order to win a daily double, it is necessary for the
purchaser of a daily double ticket to select the winners of each of the two
races specified for the double. If either of a purchaser's selections fails to
win, such purchaser's contract is void, except as hereafter
provided. Notes
